[2] Global update - Polio Eradication Initiative
Date: 18 Jun 2014
Source: Polio Eradication Initiative [edited]
http://www.polioeradication.org/Dataandmonitoring/Poliothisweek.aspx


Global Polio Eradication Initiative update as of 18 Jun 2014
-----------------------------
Wild poliovirus (WPV) cases
Total cases: Year-to-date 2014 / Year-to-date 2013 / Total 2013
Globally: 103 / 77 / 416
- in endemic countries: 91 / 46 / 160
- in non-endemic countries: 12 / 31 / 256

